pageContext.claim: “But thanks to our tireless efforts to secure the border, Border Patrol, ICE, law enforcement, incredible people, illegal crossings are down 70% since May.”
pageContext.analysis: The decline since May was nearly 70 percent, but what Trump does not say is that the rate for apprehensions and people deemed inadmissible  in October -- the most recent month available -- is about the same as a year earlier.
